    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>A jutsu designed to be like Advanced Explosive Seal, but it sacrifices the damage to disorientate enemys over larger areas. </em>You place this seal on a surface within reach, and this seal expands into a 20 foot cube. <br />  <em><strong>Activation:</strong></em> As a bonus action, you can activate this seal causing the seal to implode. All creatures in the area must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save, a target takes 4d10 Force Damage and gain 1 rank of Concussed, or only half damage and no further effect on a successful save. After this effect has been triggered the jutsu ends.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 2d10.</p>",
